data.text:
James Kay is a Partner in the Film, TV and Broadcasting Groups and head of the firm’s Media Finance Team.

James’s practice centres around the monetisation of intellectual property with a client list including private equity houses, banks, government institutions, Oscar-winning producers, rights owners and talent, including some of the world’s best-known comedians.

His telephone number is: 020 7079 0148

His email is: james.kay@sheridans.co.uk
